properties.Name: EquifaxBusinessRegistrationStatusType
properties.Description:
The status of the business on the records of the Secretary of State. It is not necessarily an indication of whether the business actively engages in business activity. It will not reflect whether the entity has fi led for bankruptcy. 

There are two valid status values: 
- Active
- Inactive
